## newstile 1.0.0 released

Forks kramdown, changes namespace from Kramdown to Newstile, adds basic newstile syntax
handling

## Changes

* New syntax:

  + You can use -. for quotation dash (auto captalize on mobile platforms)
  + You can use //. to make a full paragraph bold (lead in or summary)
  + You can use ! instead of # in headers (auto capitalize on mobile platforms)


* Deprecation notes:

  + Dash can no longer be used for bullet lists (they will be used for quotation dash in 
    a future release)
